description: Return the tags applied to an AWS Elastic Beanstalk resource. The response contains a list of tag key-value pairs. Elastic Beanstalk supports tagging of all of its resources. For details about resource tagging, see Tagging Application Resources.

parameters.name: ResourceArn
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the resouce for which a tag list is requested. Must be the ARN of an Elastic Beanstalk resource.

nested_items.name: ResourceArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the resource for which a tag list was requested.

nested_items.name: ResourceTags
nested_items.description: A list of tag key-value pairs.
